These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, ebony, black
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, daffodil
3 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, canasta
1. the person who likes black is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who likes black and the person who likes apricot##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |   3   |
| Color        | black | ebony | apricot |
| Flower         | daffodil    | dahlia     | sunflower  |
| Game   | canasta     | mah-jongg     | snooker  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, broccoli, cranberry
House: ranch-style, farmhouse, wooden
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, turquise, amber
1. the farmhouse house is the person who likes purple##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the person eating broccoli is between the person who likes amber and the person eating cauliflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |        3        |
| Food   | cauliflower    | broccoli       | cranberry             |
| House      | farmhouse  | wooden | ranch-style      |
| Color        | purple | turquise    | amber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, motorbike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, folk, hip-hop
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, broccoli, asparagus
1. the fan pop is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the fan pop is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
3. the fan pop is the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person eating watermelon is between the person driving the motorbike and the person eating asparagus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Transport           | motorbike    | scooter   | skateboard |
| Music-Genre   | folk | pop   | hip-hop         |
| Food         | broccoli     | watermelon | asparagus     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, gardening, reading
City: san-francisco, nizza, colone
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, daisy, aconite
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsaconite is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Hobby   | reading    | gardening  | puzzles     |
| City   | san-francisco       | colone   | nizza       |
| Flower     | daffodil | aconite | daisy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, swimming, baseball
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, engineer, scientist
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, purple, emerald
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the writer##1
2. the writer is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is the person who likes purple##1
4. the writer is between the engineer and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Sport   | baseball | swimming   | golf   |
| Job           | engineer   | writer | scientist     |
| Color     | ebony   | emerald    | purple |

