.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, biathlon, tennis
There 3 different types of food: mango, cabbage, papaya
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil, rose
1. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person eating cabbage and the person who growsrose##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |
| Sport         | biathlon   | climbing | tennis |
| Food   | mango | papaya      | cabbage  |
| Flower   | rose      | daffodil   | iris |

