.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-7::.
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, tower
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, green, brown
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, dannemann
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the tower house is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who likes lilac##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| House   | gothic-revival    | tower    | craftsman |
| Color         | lilac   | brown     | green     |
| Cigar     | swisher | dannemann | baccarat     |

