.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, june, march
There 3 different types of food: carrot, lettuce, onion
House: craftsman, victorian, tower
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person eating onion##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the tower house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person eating lettuce and the craftsman house##2
4. the person eating lettuce is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday         | march | july | june  |
| Food   | lettuce        | onion        | carrot |
| House         | victorian         | tower    | craftsman   |

