.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different games are played: poker, bridge, scrabble
House: victorian, ranch-style, townhouse
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, onion, eggplant
1. the person playing bridge is between the townhouse house and the person playing poker##2
2. the person eating eggplant is between the person eating strawberry and the person playing poker##2
3. the victorian house is in the middle##1
4. the townhouse house is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Game         | scrabble | bridge  | poker  |
| House         | townhouse    | victorian | ranch-style |
| Food   | strawberry    | eggplant       | onion  |

