.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, designer, architect
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, aconite, marigold
3 different pets are kept: goat, chinchilla, fish
1. the person who growsbellflower is the owner of the goat##1
2. the software-developer is between the person who growsaconite and the architect##2
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |
| Job   | designer       | software-developer         | architect      |
| Flower   | aconite | marigold       | bellflower |
| Pet         | fish     | chinchilla | goat |

