.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, teacher-climbing, cola
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, bartender, teacher
3 different games are played: go, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the bartender is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the dressmaker is between the person drinking cola and the person playing mah-jongg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |       3       |
| Beverage         | cola | 7up  | teacher-climbing |
| Job   | bartender      | dressmaker       | teacher          |
| Game         | go  | monopoly | mah-jongg        |

