House: art-deco, futuristic, craftsman
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, may, march
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the craftsman house##1
2. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the art-deco house is between the craftsman house and the person who's birthday is in march##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3       |
| Transport           | roller   | bus | van |
| House   | craftsman | art-deco     | futuristic       |
| Birthday   | may    | january | march       |

