The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, june
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, pink, turquise
1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who likes turquise and the blend-smoker##2
2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Cigar          | chaman      | swisher | blend     |
| Birthday   | november | june  | august     |
| Color         | turquise  | lilac | pink |

