The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, rose
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, december, january
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person who growsazalea is the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who growsrose and the person traveling to paris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |      2      |     3      |
| City   | paris | new-york | prague   |
| Flower           | marigold  | azalea        | rose     |
| Birthday     | february  | december   | january |

