1. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the fonseca-smoker and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3        |
| Birthday   | december | october   | august        |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk    | milk |
| Cigar   | fonseca     | aristoff | game     |

