3 different games are played: chess, poker, bridge
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, skateboard, boat
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person driving the boat is between the person who likes ivory and the person playing chess##2
3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing chess is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3     |
| Color      | ivory | ebony | mauve     |
| Game           | bridge      | poker | chess     |
| Transport   | skateboard       | boat      | car |

