.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-18::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, parkour, basketball
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, yellow, red
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, french, russian
1. the person who's sport is basketball is the french##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who likes red is between the russian and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Sport         | surfing | parkour | basketball |
| Color           | yellow   | red   | black |
| Nationality   | russian     | argentine | french   |

