.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-19::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, snake, fish
City: miami, venice, hannover
House: ranch-style, farmhouse, craftsman
1. the owner of the snake is between the person traveling to hannover and the craftsman house##2
2. the owner of the fish is the farmhouse house##1
3. the ranch-style house is the owner of the snake##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |      3       |
| Pet   | fish | snake      | dog  |
| City      | hannover   | venice   | miami      |
| House        | farmhouse     | ranch-style | craftsman |

