.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, rowing-polo, rowing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, rock, funk
3 different pets are kept: goat, cat, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan electronic##1
2. the fan funk is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing-polo is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is between the fan rock and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Sport    | rowing     | cycling     | rowing-polo |
| Music-Genre       | funk | electronic | rock |
| Pet   | horse     | goat       | cat    |

 